      <div type="description" n="monument">
        <head>Description of Monument</head>
        <p>Two <rs type="material" key="marmor">blue marble</rs> <rs type="objectType">column</rs>s (diam. <measure dim="diameter">0.53</measure> × i: H. <measure type="length" unit="metre" dim="height">0.85</measure>, ii: H.
<measure type="length" unit="metre" dim="height">3.62</measure>).</p>
      </div>

      <div type="description" n="text">
        <head>Description of Text</head>
        <p>i: Inscribed at <measure type="length" dim="none">0.37</measure> above base. ii: repaired in antiquity
at the right. Inscribed at 0.96 above the lower end.</p>
      </div>

      <div type="description" n="letters">
        <head>Description of Letters</head>
        <p>Irregular, <measure type="length" unit="metre" dim="height">0.03-0.04</measure>, lunate; very worn.</p>
      </div>

      <div type="description" n="date">
        <head>Date</head>
        <p><date notAfter="0900" notBefore="0501" cert="low">Sixth-tenth century A.D.</date> (<rs type="criteria">monogram</rs>)</p>
      </div>

      <div type="edition" lang="grc">
        <head lang="en">Edition</head>
        <cb n="i"/>
        		<ab> <lb n="1"/><orig n="unresolved"><expan><abbr><orig><g type="monogram"/></orig></abbr><supplied reason="abbreviation">αβκο</supplied></expan></orig> </ab> 
			<cb n="ii"/>        
				<ab>
	<lb n="1"/> <w lemma="εἰμί">ἐστὶν</w> <w lemma="ὁ">ἡ</w> <w lemma="εἴσοδος">εἴσοδος</w> <w lemma="ὁ">τοῦ</w> 
	<lb n="2"/> <orig n="unresolved">κ<gap dim="internal" extent="1" unit="character" reason="lost"/>ι<gap dim="internal" extent="1" unit="character" reason="lost"/><unclear reason="damage">λ</unclear>οθ<gap dim="internal" extent="1" unit="character" reason="lost"/>ατα<gap dim="internal" extent="1" unit="character" reason="lost"/>ου</orig> 
	<lb n="3"/><orig n="unresolved"><unclear reason="damage">λ</unclear>ονος</orig> <w lemma="οὗτος"><supplied reason="lost">το</supplied>ύτου</w> <gap dim="right" extent="3" reason="lost" unit="character"/></ab> 
      </div>

      <div type="apparatus">
        <head>Apparatus</head>
        <p>ii: ll. 2-3. Perhaps <foreign lang="grc"><supplied reason="lost">κ</supplied>ατὰ <supplied reason="lost">τ</supplied>οῦ <supplied reason="lost">πυ</supplied>λο͂νος <supplied reason="lost">το</supplied>ύτου</foreign>; but I cannot make out
any traces of letters before <foreign lang="grc"><unclear reason="undefined">Λ</unclear>ΟΝΟΣ</foreign> in
l. 3.</p>
      </div>

      <div type="translation">
        <head>Translation</head>
        <ab>ii. The entrance of the <gap reason="illegible"/> is <gap reason="lost" dim="right"/></ab>
      </div>

      <div type="history" n="locations"><head>Locations</head><p>Found: <rs type="found"><rs type="monuList">City, North-west</rs>: field c. 200 m  north-west of the Temple-Church,
half-buried.</rs>. Original location: <rs type="origLocation">Unknown.</rs>. Last recorded location: <rs type="lastLocation">Findspot.</rs>. </p></div>

      

      

